Package carl.abr.threads

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IOIO_thread
    Class (thread) used to open pins of the IOIO, as well as read IR values, and send pwm signals to the servo and motor of the robot.
    The main loop of the thread is executed in {static final int MIN_PWM_MOTOR = 1500;.
    Main_thread
    Main thread that runs the main loop of the app (run()).
